dct_title_s: Automobile road from San Diego to Imperial Valley
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, text (indicating grades).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, reservoirs, U.S. Aviation Field.
Indicates distances from Grant Hotel, San Diego and from El Centro.
Numbered 168 and '14 in lower left, 1 in upper left, and 98 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
